Application insights for Kubernetes cluster.
We can collect the logs into application insights and push them into log analytic workspace.
We can use Grafana/Prometheus and add workflow to add azure monitor as data source and create metrics on top of that.
We can use Kibana where we can store the logs as well as visualize it.
